comments:
Abolished 1.4.1951 and divided between the parishes of Bristol, 
    Long Ashton and Dundry. See also Table 2, notes (b) and (c).

Renamed 1.4.1974 to become the parish of Burnham on Sea & 
    Highbridge. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (g).
Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Clapton-in-Gordano. See also Table 2, note (b).
Created 1.4.1954 out of the parishes of Clapton and Portbury.
Created 1.4.1949 out of the parish of Yatton.

Abolished 1.4.1974 to become the Woodspring unparished area. See 
    also Table 2, note (a).
